                    <span>This book was such a remarkable book. It is appropriate for all ages. It is the story about a beautiful baby elephant ripped apart from her family and everything else she knew and loved.Her mother as well as the rest of the pact were slaughtered. Through her journey to survive she is taken on by a man named Bob Norris. You might have seen him before as the "Marlbro Man". <BR> Through the whole story you are strolling on an emotional rollercoaster. The bond between Bob and the elephant named Amy. He loved this animal like it was his own daughter. Trouble comes along for these two best friends. If you love books with awesome endings this is a perfect book for you. This book has one of the best endings I have ever read. To find out what happens, read "The Cowboy and his Elephant"</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Awesome book</div>
